allowedParameters.name: includeArchives
allowedParameters.description: Include entries from archived log files?

allowedParameters.name: queryText
allowedParameters.description: Limit the returned error messages to those containing the query text. (Case sensitive)

allowedParameters.name: until
allowedParameters.description:
Either 
 0. An ISO-8601 formatted string. 
 0. A millisecond timestamp value. representing the 'to' date and time to be used when querying the logs

allowedParameters.name: type
allowedParameters.description: 'clientErrors' is the only type currently supported

allowedParameters.name: since
allowedParameters.description:
Either 
 0. An ISO-8601 formatted string. 
 0. A millisecond timestamp value. representing the 'from' date and time to be used when querying the logs.

allowedParameters.name: numArchiveFiles
allowedParameters.description: The number of previous archived log files to be queried. (0 = unlimited). Defaults to 7 archive files.
